desc: Custom sized university graduation certificate frames. All frames only $59.95 and free postage. We cater for most Australian universities, including Monash University, RMIT, Swinburne, Deakin, UNSW and more.

layout.text:
You've worked hard for this. Don't settle for a graduation frame that doesn't fit correctly. Hang your graduation certificate proudly with a custom sized testamur frame, without the cost of a frame-maker.
All testamur frames only $59.95, with $5.00 flat shipping on all domestic orders.
